European Stocks Drop for Second Day on Italy Debt Concern, China Inflation

-- B y   A n d r e w   R u m m e r
-- 
2011-07-11T07:03:09Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-11/european-stocks-drop-for-second-day-on-italy-debt-concern-china-inflation.html
European stocks fell for a second
day as concern grew that the region’s debt crisis will spread to
 Italy  and  China ’s inflation surged to a three-year high.  The Stoxx Europe 600 Index declined 0.4 percent to 272.81
at 8:02 a.m. in  London .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
